query:
SELECT DISTINCT s.id, s.name
             FROM file_set fs
                INNER JOIN file_set_file_info fsfi ON fs.id = fsfi.file_set_id
                INNER JOIN file_info_system fis ON fsfi.file_info_id = fis.file_info_id
                INNER JOIN system s ON fis.system_id = s.id
             WHERE fs.id = ?
